SUMMARY:Deadline: Club Nothing: Community Music Fund
DESCRIPTION:Club Nothing is a global events series and USD 40\,000 fund fro
 m the tech brand Nothing\, supporting organisers\, artists\, and collectiv
 es creating new music experiences. The fund will award four individuals or
