DESCRIPTION:Innovate Grant awards two unrestricted USD 1\,800 grants every 
 quarter\, one to a visual artist and one to a photographer\, along with up
  to 18 honorable mentions who are featured and promoted on the organizatio
 n's website. The award is unrestricted\, so recipients can apply the funds
  toward new projects\, materials\, studio rent\, travel\, or other needs. 
 Grant cycles run four times a year (Winter\, Spring\, Summer\, and Fall). 
 Visual artists and photographers aged 18 and older from anywhere in the wo
 rld\, both US and international\, are eligible to apply. Applications requ
 ire contact details\, a grant category\, and 3 to 10 images of work\, plus
  a USD 35 application fee. The Spring 2026 cycle closed on June 18\, 2026\
 , and the Summer 2026 cycle follows on the regular quarterly schedule.\n\n
 Organisation: Innovate Artist Grants\nLocation: Online (applications accep
 ted worldwide)\nAward: USD 1\,800 unrestricted grant (two awarded per cycl
 e: one to a visual artist\, one to a photographer) USD 35 application fee\
