 . CURRENT ROUND TIMELINE: round opens 2 January\; Earlybird deadline 28 Fe
 bruary (GBP 40)\; Regular deadline 30 April (GBP 45)\; Final deadline 30 J
 une (GBP 50)\; shortlist announced 10 July\; funded films announced 17 Jul
 y.\n\nOrganisation: Genera Films\nLocation: Global\; open to short filmmak
